\"Star History Chart\" src=\"https://starchart.cc/RyanYuuki/AnymeX.svg?variant=adaptive\" width=\"370\" height=\"235\" />\n  </a>\n</details>\n\n## Official Communities\n\nJoin our communities to stay updated and contribute to the discussion:\n",
